author: Psyduck812
title: Dofus Wiki
text: Stub - The main stub page, listing all pages which have very little information. Cleanup - Pages that have most information, but are missing some details. Spell Cleanup - Subset of Cleanup. Lists all spell pages which are missing information. Monster Cleanup - Subset of Cleanup. Lists all monster pages which are missing information. Old - Pages that have not been updated after a major change and need verification. Reformat - Pages that do not meet the Wiki standards and need to be changed. Conversation - Pages that have all information needed, but are missing dialogue. Unsure - Items that are in-game, but have an unknown use.
